creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems of Pleasure by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Sonia; monkeywraith; Greg Giordano; Tomas Peter; Alex Clarke; Lian Pang; Shakira Searle; Ross Klatte; Anusha Iyer; Lani J.; Leonard Wilson; Sarah Jennings; SkyAlbatross
This is another volume in Ella Wheeler Wilcox's famous series of poetry. This volume bears the topic "pleasure". - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
